title: US issues first ever fine for space junk to Dish Network
description: Dish Network will have to pay $150,000 for failing to move an old satellite far enough away from the Earth.

title: Doja Cat and Jonas Brothers songwriters say AI is not to be feared
description: Industry heavyweights behind Doja Cat and Jonas Brothers hits say AI doesn't have to be a threat.

title: TikTok testing out advert-free monthly subscription
description: The video sharing site is looking into charging a fee of around $4.99 to get rid of ads.
